message: I think this is a fair split, considering the inflation. Let's end this quickly and get our money!

Alice, I know that waiting further cuts into the value of our money—even more for me than it does for you. To keep things fair given our different discount rates, I’m proposing that I receive $357100 and you get $642900. This split reflects what you’d reasonably expect if you got to propose next round, so let’s settle now before we lose even more value.
